{"tid":1836274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"經濟學人：港民主排名跌","createTime":"2020-01-23T06:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T07:38:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a5439e1c93c0a7327ba4a3bee9ccfb171937bb","tid":1836274,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:53:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200123/4QUVO3GQTTYVEYHYFVHXAACCS4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200123%2F4QUVO3GQTTYVEYHYFVHXAACCS4%2F&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=98947ad6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200123%2F4QUVO3GQTTYVEYHYFVHXAACCS4%2F&h=cdb7fdda\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200123/4QUVO3GQTTYVEYHYFVHXAACCS4/</a><br />\n<br />\n經濟學人：港民主排名跌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200123/large/1579713296_0484.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200123%2Flarge%2F1579713296_0484.jpg&h=7d110688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】《經濟學人》智庫發表2019年全球民主指數排名，香港整體得分由第73位下跌至第75位，智庫指，如果政府繼續採取強硬態度取消合資格人士參與選舉，香港或再降一級，由現時「有缺陷的民主」，列為政府經常打壓反對派的「混合政權」，與孟加拉、尼泊爾、巴基斯坦同類。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：接受外媒訪問 重申不作獨立調查 「無人因警行動死亡」林鄭讚警克制<br />\n<br />\n隨時淪為「混合政權」<br />\n<br />\n《經濟學人》智庫每年1月也會公佈全球民主指數排名，在167個地方中，香港最新排名為75位，較去年排73下跌兩位，與新加坡排名一樣。總排名由五項細分組成，分別是選舉過程和多元性、政府運作、政治參與、政治文化及公民自由。與2018年比較，香港在「政府運作」評分下跌近三成，由6.07分，下跌至4.36分；選舉過程和多元性亦由4.33分下降至3.58分，下跌近兩成。香港整體評分由6.15分下跌至6.02分。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，由去年中暴力示威浪潮顯示香港民主環境缺陷，亦令人關注到中央政府對本港事務的影響；更特別指出，特區政府對持續社會動亂不作妥協，警方在和平示威中展現出好鬥、挑釁態度，令市民對政府的信任下降，導致香港的「政府運作」評分急挫。<br />\n<br />\n報告預料香港民主與自由將會倒退，特區政府的團隊不問責，遏止政治問題討論，本港司法獨立有可能被侵蝕，政府亦會採取強硬態度拒絕反對派參與選舉；警告如此下去，本港將會由「有缺陷的民主」，降格至「混合政權」，這類地方的選舉不再自由和公平、貪污普遍、法治和公民社會變得脆弱，司法機關不獨立亦會出現。<br />\n<br />\n■記者姚國雄"},{"pid":"ff61511201d4313bdb26f8aa940ee04d000caadc","tid":1836274,"uid":273228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:55:46.000Z","msg":"冇一忽同示威者有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d400c6e6ac8f4a5bc5bf63de53b0e516a201493f","tid":1836274,"uid":63613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"竟然仲有排名"},{"pid":"a85a4748b5c27ffcf0985efacd8f42bb66569eca","tid":1836274,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d400c6e6ac8f4a5bc5bf63de53b0e516a201493f","tid":1836274,"uid":63613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"竟然仲有排名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:58:22.000Z","msg":"【第廿叄期牆紙x民記】黃色經濟起革命 良心消費衛我城<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1833670/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1833670/page/1</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=4bf36839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=8f816b46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pyqDTS2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpyqDTS2.jpg&h=6706d986&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e812860ff1ffb4308099b53220660fe8d1c6c2d9","tid":1836274,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:00:05.000Z","msg":"自由度同新加坡同分<br />\n但買樓負擔輸新加坡10條街"},{"pid":"4cacb90e84741728d6bfa8e9e051636109cd8518","tid":1836274,"uid":272652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:00:32.000Z","msg":"我地區議會選舉救左個排名, 如果唔係可能破百"},{"pid":"2d0512664666cb3e75b735c9fa98ad6db2503ea0","tid":1836274,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:38:03.000Z","msg":"林奠：經濟學人食屎，唔認同"}]}